          },
          "reviewBody": "The prima facie of every school or that taken into consideration, every place,are their people. And so are the students of THE CALCUTTA BOYS'SCHOOL. With their extreme talent to excel in every field, to emceeing the oldest and the most prestigious school fest of Kolkata - The Concord. Needless to mention it is the very best school of Kolkata, with amazing people in it and the ofcourse the grandeur of the Britishers being eminent in every foot.\nA for Apple, B for Ball, C for CBS, Best of All.",
          "publisher": {
